### Python Installation in Ubuntu
##Method 1:
#Step 1: Update your local system's repository list
   sudo apt update
#Step 2: Download the latest version of Python
   sudo apt install python3
   
##Method 2:
#Step 1: Install the mentioned package on your system
   sudo apt install software-properties-common
#Step 2:Add the official Deadsnakes PPA link to your system's repository list
   sudo add-apt-repository ppa:deadsnakes/ppa
#Step 3:Update your system's package list
   sudo apt update
#Step 4:Download the latest version of Python from the added PPA
   sudo apt install python3
   
##Check for the Python version
   python3 --version
